title: Does the Google Pixel 2 support other UBS-C to headphone jack dongles than the original?
content: Does the Google Pixel 2 support other UBS-C to Headphone adapters other than the original? Or, does someone know where I can buy an original adapter that can be delivered to the Netherlands? My original adapter is broken and other adapters that I tried are not supported/recognized by the device. Thanks in advance.
